oggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ihg1665702642922.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ihg1665702642922.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ihg1665702642922.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ihg1665702642922\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                              \n GFPRendering \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this property to control whether the web page content in the HTML widget is rendered in the Canvas.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__topic_d104207e1_d104208e1_d104209e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__p_d104210e1_d104211e1_d104212e1\">GFPRendering\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__section_w46ab1b5b3_w47ab1b5_w48ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__2\">\n Do not render web page content in the Canvas.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1__entry__2\">\n Render the content of the web page specified in the Base URL property.\n <div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__note_w49ab1b5b3b1b3b7b3b3b1_w50ab1b5b3b1b3b7b3b3_w51ab1b5b3b1b3b7b3_w52ab1b5b3b1b3b7_w53ab1b5b3b1b3_w54ab1b5b3b1_w55ab1b5b3_w56ab1b5_w57ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Not recommended. Rendering the content affects the performance of the Canvas and poses a security risk if malicious JavaScript is executed.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__section_yhd_wwb_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1224656e127\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__table_d12302e1_d12303e1_d12304e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__section_sdz_xwb_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1224656e176\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__p_d104219e1_d104220e1_d104221e1\">This property is provided for compatibility with\n            versions of Uniface prior to Uniface 9.7.02.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__section_kjk_zwb_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1224656e185\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__ul_crj_1xb_xwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihg1665702642922__li_d41522e1_d41523e1_d41524e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdu1665702642851.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Base URL (BaseURL)</a><p>Defines the base URL used to find the related resources of the HTML widget. The value can be a directory or file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613694\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613694\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GFPRendering Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 GFPRendering Use this property to control whether the web page content in the HTML widget is rendered in the Canvas. GFPRendering = | False | True Value Description False Do not render web page content in the Canvas. True Render the content of the web page specified in the Base URL property. CAUTION: Not recommended. Rendering the content affects the performance of the Canvas and poses a security risk if malicious JavaScript is executed. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Base URL Description This property is provided for compatibility with versions of Uniface prior to Uniface 9.7.02. Applies To uhtml (HTML Widget) Related Links Base URL (BaseURL) Defines the base URL used to find the related resources of the HTML widget. The value can be a directory or file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}